snippet.title: A New HOME - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After 3 years of development since the 2.0 English Translation release of OFF, HOME is finally finished. Join The Judge in his quest to save the world from its impending doom in the most anticipated fanmade Spinoff of OFF.

You can find Felix's blog and Youtube Channel here:
http://thejudge.tumblr.com/
https://www.youtube.com/user/FelixFel...

Download the game here:
http://rpgmaker.net/games/6361/

Song - Pure Imagination by Maroon 5:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OTc3o...

Go support the people involved in this project:
https://theartofscarecrows.tumblr.com...
http://winsdayink.tumblr.com/
http://p4zam.tumblr.com/tagged/pazam-...
http://chimakiisane.tumblr.com
http://sesakamonster.tumblr.com
http://Needsmorebirds.tumblr.com
http://tigerman9001.tumblr.com
http://eviefang.tumblr.com
http://zira361.tumblr.com

Rest In Peace, Felix. We miss you dearly.
